s website.       Resources      Please review these important resources which help you meet your career goals during your time at UIC.    4 Year Checklist    Career Planning Guide    Upcoming Career Events (fairs, workshops)    Career Education Resources         Career Exploration      If you want to know more about how majors connect to careers, visit our Career Exploration page for advice and tips.    Career Exploration         Career Advising      If you want to work with one of our Career Adviser or learn more about what advising can provide to you, visit our Career Advising page.    Career Advising    Schedule an Advising Appointment         Jobs & Internships      If you are searching for a job or internship opportunities as a student or alumni, visit the UICcareers website .  If you want to learn about job search, visit our Jobs page.  If you want to learn about internships and how completing internships can benefit your career goals visit our Internships page.    UICcareers.com    Jobs    Internships         Resumes      If you want to create strong resumes, CVs, and cover letters , review our guidance on these documents including sample resumes and cover letters.    Resumes/CVs/Cover Letters         Interviews      If you want to learn how to ace upcoming interviews and networking , review our tips pages.    Interviews    Networking         Student Success      Learn about what successful UIC alumni are doing and the journeys they took for their success.    Student Success Stories    Graduate Outcomes            Students    Back to main content           Career Programs and Events    Career Advising    Career Exploration     Career Education Resources      Resumes, CVs, and Cover Letters    Interviews    Jobs    Internships    Networking    Student Success Stories     Graduate Outcomes    Journey to Success Nomination Form                    UIC Logo        Career Services         Students    Career Planning Guide    Make an Appointment    FAQs      Employe